      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This car is in truly mint condition, looking and driving exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. With a flawless exterior and a pristine interior, it\u2019s a rare find for any enthusiast looking for a vehicle that has been meticulously maintained.",
