      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably maintained specimen, curated for the most discerning automotive enthusiast. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that is truly exemplary. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every detail reflects a standard of care synonymous with concours-level quality. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned market, offering an uncompromising aesthetic and mechanical profile.",
