    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car has been babied since day one\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it still has that fresh feel inside and out. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for something that's been cared for with a ton of love, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come see this beauty in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
