      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time capsule' specimen that defines the standard for collector-grade quality. This vehicle has been curated with obsessive attention to detail, resulting in a condition that rivals its original delivery day. The exterior paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a multi-layer professional ceramic coating; you will find no rock chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. The wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in a fresh set of premium performance tires. Inside, the cabin is immaculate. The leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers, and I possess a comprehensive binder of every service receipt from day one. It has been stored year-round in a climate-controlled garage under a breathable car cover and has never seen rain or snow. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire an investment-grade vehicle that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
