      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of its model line. It has been preserved to an exacting standard, showing no discernible signs of previous use. Every surface and mechanical system reflects a history of meticulous stewardship, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original manufacture. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a truly pristine specimen.",
      "price": 44500.0,
